wt.occurrence

Interface PathOccurrenceContext

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    _BaselineConfigurationVersion, BaselineConfigurationVersion
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    _MPMPlant, _MPMResource, _MPMResourceGroup, _WTPart, MPMPlant, MPMResource, MPMResourceGroup, WTPart

    @GenAsPersistable(interfaces=Versionable.class,
                  extendable=true)
public interface PathOccurrenceContext
    This tagging interface allows classes of objects to provide the context for PathOccurrences (and CombinedPathOccurrences).

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
